TITLE: Kalki Avatar | What Avatar Doing Nowadays | Blessings For Avatara Army Force | Universal Message
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7JQ1IMDBjw
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Noor Ananta provides a candid update on Kalki's current state after completing a long phase of intense kriyas. She reveals that Kalki has been given a rest period -- for the first time in their life, they can exercise their own will: wake up, sleep, eat, wear clothes, watch movies, go shopping, or simply enjoy music at their own discretion. During the entire process period, everything was dictated by the cosmic process, leaving zero personal choice. The universe has instructed: "Rest now, because ahead lies the real physical-world battle."

She explains that while the cosmic world Mahabharat has concluded, the physical-world leela (divine play) is about to begin with face-to-face encounters. She extends blessings to Kalki's army, noting that they too will receive a brief rest period through cosmic synchronicity -- when Kalki rests, the connected army members also get a pause. She candidly states that Kalki also has no money, but the universe provides small amounts for basic needs, and the same will happen for the army.

She reiterates that this channel operates in "cosmic language" (coding), not bookish knowledge -- those with traditional religious education will not understand anything here. Only those who understand the language of energy, the cosmic world, and God's coding language will comprehend. The chosen ones are specifically those with ZERO traditional knowledge -- atheists, common workers, auto drivers -- not babas, gurus, or scholars.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Kalki is currently in a rare rest period after completing the cosmic-world Mahabharat; for the first time ever, exercising personal will
- The real physical-world battle/leela is about to begin with face-to-face encounters -- everything so far was cosmic-realm processing
- Kalki also has no money; the universe provides minimally as needed -- the same applies to all army members
- The channel operates in cosmic coding language, not bookish knowledge; traditional scholars will never understand its content
- Dattreya energy was assigned the task of spreading Kalki's message from 2019, connecting with chosen ones who are all atheists/common people

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: The transition from cosmic war to physical-world manifestation -- Kalki's cosmic Mahabharat is complete, and the brief rest period precedes the real-world leela where the avatar and army will face the physical-world challenges of establishing the new age.

